 on:\n    - NYC Reversal (FL-006)\n    - Three-Level Expansion (FL-005)\n    - Fibonacci Rejection Zones\n    If the tool returns no data, tell Steve to check if the specific manual is indexed.\"\"\"\n)"}]}]},"metadata":{"duetProject":"cloudshell-gca","ideName":"Code OSS for Cloud Shell","ideType":"CLOUD_SHELL","ideVersion":"1.104.3-cde","platform":"LINUX_AMD64","pluginType":"CLOUD_CODE","pluginVersion":"2.72.0"},"project":"cloudshell-gca","requestId":"cloudcode-871671220-8f14a5b9-be0a-4bff-839c-eb815c66b40e","userContext":{}}
